&lt;p&gt;Newham Medical Centre is currently looking to welcome an experienced practice nurse to join the team. We are a friendly, innovative and supportive practice with a list size of 10150.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our team currently consists of 3 GP Partners, 3 Salaried GP’s, Nurse, HCA and Clinical Pharmacists. We are a training practice with medical students.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are ideally looking for a practice nurse who has experience of working within primary care and looking to provide proactive care for our patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Salary is negotiable and will be based on experience.&lt;/p&gt;
